a335c10b863c62831edce1c92103afcee93cd75e.query:
insert into npc_replies (pattern, template, channel, to_mention, enabled, created_by) values
            ("^!twitter$", $3, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!youtube$", $4, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!clips$", $5, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!vod(?:s)?(?:-)?(?:channel)?(?:s)?$", $6, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!reddit$", "reddit.com/r/PedroPeepos", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!discord$", $7, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!instagram$", $8, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!tiktok$", $9, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!social(?:s)?$", $10, $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!stream$|\s*stream(?:ing)?\s+(?:today|now)\s*\?.*)$", "No stream on Wednesday, Caedrel has EUphoria & Riot meetings. Stream should be back on Thursday. Follow twitter.com/caedrelupdates for more updates ok", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("(?:^!cast$|^!lec$|\s*cast(?:ing|in)?\s+(?:lec\s+)?(?:today|tonight)(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+(?:on\+s)?(?:today|tonight)(?:\?)?|\s*lec\s+on(?:\?)?|\s+at\s+lec\s+(?:today|tonight)(?:\?)?)", "No LEC today Sadge LEC will be back the 15th, 16th and 17th of April. You can find LEC schedule here lolesports.com/schedule?leagues=lec", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!end(?:ing)?(?:-)?song$", "okaywill - Chicken Dinner: youtube.com/watch?v=B_rAI7zaVZU", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!(?:nord)?(?:-)?vpn$", "Get NordVPN here nordvpn.com/caedrel, 30-day money-back guarantee with coupon code 'Caedrel' upon checkout", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!emote(?:s)?$", "To see emotes install 7TV 7tv.app. These are Caedrel's emotes: 7tv.app/users/61e2b8461f8f9d5cf63321a1", $2, 0, 1, $1),
            ("^!(?:prime(?:(?:-)?sub(?:s)?)?|sub(?:s(?:cribe)?)?)$", "You can sub to Caedrel's channel and use your Twitch Prime here twitch.tv/subs/caedrel", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            ("^!time$", "It's {{ format_date_time('now', '%I:%M %p', 'Europe/Berlin') }} in Caedrel's timezone", $2, 0, 1, $1),

            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:caedALLO|peepoSitHey|good\s+morning)(:?\s+)?.*", "caedALLO", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:thanks|thank\s+you|thnx|ty)(?:\s+)?.*$", "ok", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:GIGACHAD|best\s+mod|good\s+mod|PETTHEMODS|<3|heart|love)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:bye)(?:\s+)?.*", "bye", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Pog|PogU|POGGIES|POGGERS|caedPog)(?:\s+)?.*", "xddFlush", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:xdd.*)(?:\s+)?.*", "widexddL", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:Aware|TrollAware|TrollDespair|Despairge|xddDespair)(?:\s+)?.*", "Aware Despairge", $2, 1, 0, $1),
            (".*(?:\s+)?(?:DonoWall)(?:\s+)?.*", "classic DonoWall Despair", $2, 1, 0, $1);

b25ce0464a18f3685e62f37d6c97399934f06987.query:
select
                    id,
                    pattern,
                    case_insensitive,
                    template,
                    to_mention,
                    channel,
                    enabled,
                    created_by,
                    created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                    updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
                from npc_replies
                where enabled = 1 and (channel is null or channel = $1)
                order by id asc
